+    "date-fns": "^2.24.0",
+    "react": "17.0.2",
+    "react-native": "0.65.1",
+    "react-native-agora": "^3.4.6",
+    "react-native-callkeep": "^4.2.0",
+    "react-native-chart-kit": "^6.11.0",
+    "react-native-document-picker": "^6.0.4",
+    "react-native-gesture-handler": "^1.10.3",

+    "react-native-web": "^0.17.1",
+    "react-native-webview": "^11.13.0"
+  },
+  "devDependencies": {
+    "@babel/core": "^7.12.9",
+    "@babel/runtime": "^7.12.5",
+    "@react-native-community/eslint-config": "^2.0.0",
+    "babel-jest": "^26.6.3",

+    "metro-react-native-babel-preset": "^0.66.0",

+    "preset": "react-native"
+  }
+}

{
  "name": "clarondocdoctor",
  "version": "0.0.1",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {
    "android": "react-native run-android",
    "ios": "react-native run-ios --port 8082 --simulator='iPhone 12 Pro Max'",
    "pods": "npx pod-install ios",
    "clean": "watchman watch-del-all",
    "start": "react-native start --reset-cache",
    "test": "jest",
    "lint": "eslint ."
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@eva-design/eva": "^2.1.1",
    "@react-native-async-storage/async-storage": "^1.15.7",
    "@react-native-firebase/app": "^12.8.0",

    "@react-navigation/native-stack": "^6.1.0",
    "@react-navigation/stack": "^6.0.7",
    "@ui-kitten/components": "^5.1.1",
    "@ui-kitten/eva-icons": "^5.1.1",
    "axios": "^0.21.1",
    "date-fns": "^2.24.0",
    "react": "17.0.2",
    "react-native": "0.65.1",
    "react-native-agora": "^3.4.6",
    "react-native-callkeep": "^4.2.0",
    "react-native-chart-kit": "^6.11.0",
    "react-native-document-picker": "^6.0.4",
    "react-native-gesture-handler": "^1.10.3",
    "react-native-safe-area-context": "^3.3.0",
    "react-native-screens": "^3.6.0",
    "react-native-svg": "^12.1.1",
    "react-native-uuid": "^2.0.1",
    "react-native-voip-push-notification": "^3.3.0",
    "react-native-web": "^0.17.1",
    "react-native-webview": "^11.13.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@babel/core": "^7.12.9",
    "@babel/runtime": "^7.12.5",
    "@react-native-community/eslint-config": "^2.0.0",
    "babel-jest": "^26.6.3",
    "eslint": "7.14.0",
    "jest": "^26.6.3",
    "metro-react-native-babel-preset": "^0.66.0",
    "react-native-codegen": "^0.0.7",
    "react-test-renderer": "17.0.2"
  },
  "jest": {
    "preset": "react-native"
  }
}
